'''敘利亞人軍事委員會'''（{{Lang-syr| ܡܘܬܒܐ ܦܘܠܚܝܐ ܣܘܪܝܝܐ}}，[[拉丁转写|拉丁转写]]：Mawtbo Fulhoyo Suryoyo，缩写为MFS；{{Lang-ar|المجلس العسكري السرياني السوري}}）是一支敘利亞[[亚述人|亚述人]]的軍事組織。於2013年1月1日宣布成立，目標為挺身爭取亞述人的民族權力，以及保護居住在敘利亞的亞述人。<ref><cite class="citation web" contenteditable="false">Khalel, Sheren; Vickery, Matthew (24 February 2015). </cite></ref> 主要在亞述人口密度較高的[[哈塞克省|哈塞克省]]作戰<ref><cite class="citation web" contenteditable="false">[http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syriacs-establish-military-council-in-syria.aspx?pageID=238&nid=40329 "Syriacs establish military council in Syria"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syriacs-establish-military-council-in-syria.aspx?pageID=238&nid=40329 |date=20141006125944 }}. </cite></ref>

2013年12月16日，敘利亞人軍事委員會宣稱建立了一所新的軍校，名為「阿布加烈士」（Martyr Abgar）。<ref><cite class="citation web" contenteditable="false">[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wW4un8kx1ZM "The Academy Martyr Abgar (Sohdo Abgar) of Syriac Military Council was founded!"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wW4un8kx1ZM |date=20151123205620 }}</cite></ref><ref><cite class="citation web" contenteditable="false">[https://www.facebook.com/SYRIACMILITARYCOUNCIL?ref=ts&fref=ts "Welcome to Facebook - Log In, Sign Up or Learn More"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.facebook.com/SYRIACMILITARYCOUNCIL?ref=ts&fref=ts |date=20210110204442 }}. </cite></ref>12月24日，MFS公佈了一系列照片以證明他們控制了卡塔尼亞(Qahtaniyah)以南8公里的小鎮革祖卡(Ghardukah)。<ref><cite class="citation web" contenteditable="false">[https://twitter.com/MarthaVergili/status/415557140376723456 "Martha Vergili-Hobil on Twitter: "Mor Malke in Gharduka is destroyed by El-Nusra. ] {{Wayback|url=https://twitter.com/MarthaVergili/status/415557140376723456 |date=20140121150658 }}</cite></ref> 小鎮的教會先前已經完全被[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]摧毀，直到10月中[[人民保护部队|人民保护部队]]（YPG）和MFS發動攻擊將他們驅逐出去。<ref><cite class="citation news" contenteditable="false">[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l99iQaDH7e8 "Sher Tirbesipi"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l99iQaDH7e8 |date=20150321092224 }} (in Kurdish). </cite></ref> 2014年1月8日，MFS宣稱他們加入了YPG的隊伍。<ref>[https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=304163833070914&set=a.295534343933863.1073741829.295031123984185&type=1&theater The #Syriac Military Council has joined the YPG!] </ref><ref>[http://diclenews.com/2/22/viewNews/379648 Syriac Military Council: Most important decisions is to join YPG] {{Wayback|url=http://diclenews.com/2/22/viewNews/379648 |date=20170907124345 }} Dicle News Agency, 9 January 2014</ref>

== 布拉克遺址和泰勒哈米斯行動 ==
從2013年12月26日在[[泰勒哈米斯|泰勒哈米斯]](Tel Hamis)區域開始，MFS是以YPG為首的聯盟的一部分, 共同對抗[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]和[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]] (ISIL)。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LHjLsXhtpvA|title=Interview with Christian SMC fighters and local Sunni Arabs who fights along YPG and YPJ|work=YouTube|date=3 January 2014|accessdate=12 October 2014|archive-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427063820/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LHjLsXhtpvA|dead-url=no}}</ref> 但YPG和MFS並沒能守住[[布拉克遺址|布拉克遺址]](Tell Brak)，到隔年1月初攻勢取消為止，也沒有攻下[[泰勒哈米斯|泰勒哈米斯]]。直到2月23日一次拂曉夜襲，YPG和MFS成功從當地阿拉伯部落手中攻下[[布拉克遺址|布拉克遺址]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/02/22/us-syria-crisis-town-idUSBREA1L0IJ20140222|title=Syrian Kurds take town from Islamists: watchdog|work=Reuters|date=22 February 2014|accessdate=12 October 2014|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120191324/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/02/22/us-syria-crisis-town-idUSBREA1L0IJ20140222|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 六月反攻（敘利亞 - 伊拉克邊境） ==
MFS隨著YPG參與了沿著敘利亞伊拉克邊境的進攻，試圖逐出[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]的勢力。伊斯蘭國在[[2014年伊拉克北部內戰|2014年伊拉克北部內戰]]中控制了[[摩蘇爾|摩蘇爾]]和[[尼尼微省|尼尼微省]]大部分地區。這次行動在邊境的[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]側成功控制了[[提爾可卡|提爾可卡]](Til-Koçar)，在邊境的[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]側成功控制了[[拉比耶|拉比耶]](Rabia)。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.syriacsnews.com/presence-mfs-border-iraq/|title=Presence of the MFS at the border of Iraq|work=Syriac International News Agency|date=16 June 2014|accessdate=12 October 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006172212/http://www.syriacsnews.com/presence-mfs-border-iraq/|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1KKDpfj4o1w&feature=youtu.be|title=‫أراء مقاتلي وحدات حماية الشعب في بلدة ربيعة - YouTube|work=YouTube|date=16 June 2014|accessdate=12 October 2014|archive-date=2015-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151218101801/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1KKDpfj4o1w&feature=youtu.be|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 八月反攻（尼尼微和辛賈爾） ==
MFS隨著YPG和其他同盟參加了在[[尼尼微省|尼尼微省]][[辛賈爾|辛賈爾]]區的攻勢，以防止少數民族遭受[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]攻擊。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.frequency.com/video/ypg-mfs-arrived-in-shingal-mountains/185402086?cid=5-618|title=Video: YPG and MFS arrived in Shingal Mountains Sinjar to protect the refugees who fled from Shingal and other Towns|work=Frequency|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809191217/http://www.frequency.com/video/ypg-mfs-arrived-in-shingal-mountains/185402086?cid=5-618|archivedate=2014年8月9日|df=}}</ref>

== 哈布爾谷行動 ==
[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]在2015年2月末發起一連串針對哈塞克省東北的哈布爾河谷(Khabur river valley)內基督徒村莊的攻擊，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.christiantoday.com/article/assyrian.christian.leaders.call.for.help.against.renewed.isis.offensive.in.hassakeh/49749.htm|title=Assyrian Christian leaders call for help against renewed ISIS offensive in Hassakeh|work=Christian Today|date=11 March 2015|accessdate=16 March 2015|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923203111/http://www.christiantoday.com/article/assyrian.christian.leaders.call.for.help.against.renewed.isis.offensive.in.hassakeh/49749.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>並意圖奪取YPG和MFS所控制的戰略重鎮[[泰爾坦默|泰爾坦默]](Tel Tamer)。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aleteia.org/en/world/article/christian-area-in-northeast-syria-said-to-be-under-heavy-isis-assault-5872546100543488|title=Christian Area in Northeast Syria Said to Be Under Heavy ISIS Assault|date=7 March 2015|accessdate=16 March 2015|archive-date=2015-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150808123347/http://www.aleteia.org/en/world/article/christian-area-in-northeast-syria-said-to-be-under-heavy-isis-assault-5872546100543488|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年3月初，[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]與MFS和YPG的部隊在[[特爾納斯里|特爾納斯里]](Tel Nasri)和[[泰爾瑪斯|泰爾瑪斯]](Tel Mghas)地區的村莊爆發激烈衝突。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aina.org/news/20150307144915.htm|title=ISIS Crosses River in New Attacks on Assyrian Villages in Syria|date=7 March 2015|accessdate=16 March 2015|archive-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427063858/http://www.aina.org/news/20150307144915.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年3月15日，MFS宣稱已經收復了[[泰爾瑪斯|泰爾瑪斯]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/SyriacMFS/status/577233424018182144|title=MFS and YPG liberated the church [of Tel Mghas] and are present there now|date=15 March 2015|accessdate=16 March 2015|archive-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427063901/https://twitter.com/SyriacMFS/status/577233424018182144|dead-url=no}}</ref>

